items.title: Stock Market LIVE Updates: GIFT Nifty indicates a gap-down start; US markets flat, Asia mixed
items.description: Sensex Today | Stock Market LIVE Updates: The S&P 500 ended little changed on Wednesday, with technology shares gaining but investors nervous about Middle East tensions and more U.S. labor data due this week. The Dow Jones Industrial Average rose 39.55 points, or 0.09%, to 42,196.52. The S&P 500 gained 0.79 points, or 0.01%, at 5,709.54 and the Nasdaq Composite edged up 14.76 points, or 0.08%, to 17,925.12.
